Also transmission mount, water pump (rotted/corroded), and wheel lug nuts (these 3 items not covered). M.P.

notes.note: Called shop to get better understanding of why so many items were needed in front end. Both front ball joint have play, left front wheel bearing extremely loose. Loose bearing caused splines on left front cv shaft to wear. Wear at inner cv shaft where intermediate shaft enters (on both sides), wear on intermediate shaft on both sides. Did confirm that right front outer cv boot is torn, but shaft needs to be replaced due to wear internally at inner joint, where it connects to stub shaft. Very common issue on Dodge's. Proceeding with claim for covered portion of repair. M.P.
